Authors@R: person("Miguel", "Rodo", email = "miguel.rodo@uct.ac.za", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A command-line tool for managing multiple related Git repositories as a unified workspace.
    Provides wrappers for Bash scripts that handle multi-repository management, Git worktrees,
    VS Code integration, and pipeline execution.
